title: Paul McCartney 2016-08-18 The Q, Cleveland, Ohio
description:
Here is a very nice recent bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Got tickets released at the last minute, 
49 bucks for lower level!!  My first 
McCartney since 1990.  Video is pretty 
good.  Seats are very cramped with knees 
hitting the rail in front so I had to 
readjust often as you will see.  Good news 
is that I was in the middle of the row and 
in first row so nobody in fron and no 
bathroom people walking in front of me.  
I havent had time to watch and won't because 
I have a busy weekend planned and wanted 
to post for you all.  Sound is never great 
from my camera but video is usually pretty 
good.  As always, do whatever you want with 
my videos.  Post them, share them, dub audio, 
eat them or screw them!  Just tray and enjoy!
My GF Sue took the pics while I did video so thanks to her!
